apps.mtdesktop.fileutility
Interface FileTransferListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
DesktopFrame, TableRadar, TabletopTreeController, Test
public interface FileTransferListener

The listener interface for receiving fileTransfer events. The class that is interested in processing a fileTransfer event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addFileTransferListener method. When the fileTransfer event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.

See Also:
FileTransferEvent
